Task 1 : Publish the JUnit test report with "Archive Junit formatted test results"  for spring petclinic application. Test Report xml as "target/surefire-reports/TEST-*.xml"
Use junit 'target/sure-fire-reports/Test-*.xml'

Task 2: Use HTML Publisher plugin and publish HTML reports
Generate snippet for Publish HTML Reports
HTML directory "target/site/jacoco"
Use publishHTML([allowMissing: false, alwaysLinkToLastBuild: false, keepAll: false, reportDir: 'target/site/jacoco', reportFiles: 'index.html', reportName: 'HTML Report', reportTitles: ''])

Task3 : Back up Jenkins
Perform the command in .jenkins folder in your home directory
 tar -czf jenkins_home.tgz jenkins/
 ls
 tar -tzf jenkins_home.tgz | head
 scp
 tar -xzf jenkins_home.tgz
 Copy the installation file to the target system
 and do java -jar jenkins.war that make use of Jenkins folder



